Family fishing at Lac Dumoulin Outfitter:
Family fishing at Lac Dumoulin Outfitter. Imagine yourself on an island, in the middle of a lake with clear waters. Sandy beaches, outdoor games and a caressing breeze (which eliminates flies). Come live the Dumoulin adventure!
Lac Dumoulin Outfitter is located 20 minutes from La Tuque on Route 25, in the middle of the large 100 square kilometer Lake Dumoulin, the centerpiece of the domain.
Upon your arrival, you will start your trip with a short pontoon cruise to the island. You can then make yourself comfortable in one of our cozy waterfront cottages. They range in size from 2 to 12 people and are known for their cleanliness. Each cottage is carefully checked before your arrival.
The activities offered will satisfy you in summer as well as in winter. With its 32 lakes, 15 of which are open year round, the outfitter offers an incredible variety of fish species. We take great care of our lakes to ensure a superior quality of fishing. You will have a recent motorized boat, by 2 adults. To get to the lakes, the outfitter has developed several trails where you can choose to ride an ATV or walk to your fishing spot.
After a good day of fishing, the staff of the outfitter will take care of your catch while you plan a good meal. You will be cordially invited, if needed, to our beautiful lodge to enjoy a nice warm meal. You can also simply use the facilities of your cottage to prepare a feast like at home.
In winter, the place becomes an essential snowmobile stopover! We offer lodging in one of our magnificent 4 season cottages. At the inn, you can enjoy a good meal or a drink in a warm environment.
